      public static EncryptedIndexWithStash calculateEncryptedCTIndex(int tableSize, int numberOfValues, Map<Label,Set<Plaintext>> multiMap, SecretKey prfKey, SEScheme seScheme) throws IOException
      Parameters:
      tableSize - the size of the tables
      numberOfValues - the number of values stored in the multimap
      multiMap - the multimap containing the plaintext data
      prfKey - the secret key used for the PRF
      seScheme - the symmetric encryption scheme
      Returns:
      the encrypted index of the counter tables calculated with Cuckoo Hashing, the tables are encrypted, the stash is not.
      Throws:
      IOException
